{"tid":55321,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"林一鳴 十大經濟預言","createTime":"2016-12-26T10:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T13:43:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03f257eb01776803c60a7345620ad4018adbb236","tid":55321,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/180250_a2c1c651fbc61f92e6e2cb0e27444ebe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F180250_a2c1c651fbc61f92e6e2cb0e27444ebe.jpg&h=b5517e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一.「美國評級下降，美元貶值。」<br />\n<br />\n二.「中國外匯儲備將逐步減少美元及美債，部分更以黃金取代。」<br />\n<br />\n三.「部分國家重新執行金本位制度。」<br />\n<br />\n四.「金價大幅攀升，在數年時間之內，將升逾每盎司2,000美元。」<br />\n<br />\n五.「商品牛市未完，商品牛市將持續10年以上，導致通脹失控。」<br />\n<br />\n六.「投資銀行捲土重來，而且賭得更加利害。」<br />\n<br />\n七.「美國國債價格下降。」<br />\n<br />\n八.「人民幣自由浮動，成為國際貨幣。」<br />\n<br />\n九.「港元與美元脫勾，然後與人民幣掛勾。」<br />\n<br />\n十.「中國取代美國的全球經濟領導地位。」"},{"pid":"d3957b2093ac344e2a085424056394346510ad53","tid":55321,"uid":9375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:11:59.000Z","msg":"佢好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5556152442ccccadb63a36b34cbcc3943a92b4","tid":55321,"uid":22531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/180250_a2c1c651fbc61f92e6e2cb0e27444ebe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F180250_a2c1c651fbc61f92e6e2cb0e27444ebe.jpg&h=b5517e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一.「美國評級下降，美元貶值。」<br />\n<br />\n二.「中國外匯儲備將逐步減少美元及美債，部分更以黃金取代。」<br />\n<br />\n三.「部分國家重新執行金本位制度。」<br />\n<br />\n四.「金價大幅攀升，在數年時間之內，將升逾每盎司2,000美元。」<br />\n<br />\n五.「商品牛市未完，商品牛市將持續10年以上，導致通脹失控。」<br />\n<br />\n六.「投資銀行捲土重來，而且賭得更加利害。」<br />\n<br />\n七.「美國國債價格下降。」<br />\n<br />\n八.「人民幣自由浮動，成為國際貨幣。」<br />\n<br />\n九.「港元與美元脫勾，然後與人民幣掛勾。」<br />\n<br />\n十.「中國取代美國的全球經濟領導地位。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無timeline,我夠識預言世界會滅亡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669cdb95f07a0b790fbb104c00050c14cc11badb","tid":55321,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"無source 你話Steve Job講都得喇"},{"pid":"71e025c91abb9fad239244da3f5428162edc5683","tid":55321,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"仆街同我諗法差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a374d1d872e5c409a6c14b6275a2c94034713c1c","tid":55321,"uid":9375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街同我諗法差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac869bc432aeff113b18d2591ed69ce419a5565","tid":55321,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"真係全部反轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ae082ed2b059c2646ed5f253fd71d0b457744c","tid":55321,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係全部反轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ba523a1d58a8053b0